ja-cat-responds-losing-followers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-responds-losing-followers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-responds-losing-followers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>多<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">贾·猫 (Doja Cat)</a>表示，看到大量人在社交媒体上取消关注她，让她感到“自由”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/doja-cat-planet-her-review-2978431">Doja Cat – “Planet Her”评论：备受争议的流行说唱歌手进入她的帝国阶段</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.complex.com/music/a/alex-ocho/doja-cat-responds-half-a-million-fans-unfollowing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">据报道</a>，这位洛杉矶说唱歌手兼歌手在过去几周里在 Instagram 上失去了大约 50 万粉丝， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-calls-out-fans-for-calling-themselves-kittenz-calls-it-creepy-3472563">因为她称自己的粉丝“令人毛骨悚然”</a> ，因为她给自己贴上了粉丝名字“Kittenz”的标签。</p><p>在一系列后来被删除的推文中，这位明星写道：“我的粉丝不能给自己起名字。如果你称自己为‘小猫’或他妈的‘小猫’，那就意味着你需要放下手机，找份工作，帮助父母料理家务。”</p><p>据报道，在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-loses-180k-instagram-followers-and-deletes-threads-after-lashing-out-at-fans-3473069">开始失去数十万粉丝</a>之前，几个粉丝账户被停用。 </p><figure id="attachment_3437971" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3437971" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3437971" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/doja-cat-met-gala@2000x1270.jpg" alt="多哈猫" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/doja-cat-met-gala@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/doja-cat-met-gala@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/doja-cat-met-gala@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/doja-cat-met-gala@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/doja-cat-met-gala@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/doja-cat-met-gala@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3437971" class="wp-caption-text"> Doja Cat 在 2023 年 Met Gala 上。图片来源：Sipa USA / Alamy Stock Photo</figcaption></figure><p>现在，Doja Cat 已经对取消关注的热潮做出了回应，目前她的 Instagram 粉丝数量已达 2510 万。</p><p>她在 Instagram 故事中写道：“看到所有这些人取消关注，让我感觉自己已经打败了一头长期以来一直压制着我的野兽，感觉我可以与真正重要和爱我的人重新建立联系。”为了我是谁，而不是为了我曾经是谁。”</p><p>她补充道：“我感到自由。” </p><figure id="attachment_3484300" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484300" style="width: 1284px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3484300" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-feels-free-instagram-unfollowing.jpg" alt="多哈猫 Instagram 故事" width="1284" height="2203" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-feels-free-instagram-unfollowing.jpg 1284w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-feels-free-instagram-unfollowing-400x686.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-feels-free-instagram-unfollowing-800x1373.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-feels-free-instagram-unfollowing-696x1194.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/doja-cat-feels-free-instagram-unfollowing-1068x1832.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1284px) 100vw, 1284px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484300" class="wp-caption-text">多贾·猫 (Doja Cat) 表示，在失去数十万粉丝后，她感到“自由”了（图片来源：Instagram）</figcaption></figure><p>在这位歌手发布第一条推文后，一位粉丝指出了这种明显的虚伪，并提醒这位音乐家，她是提出“小猫”一词的人。多贾猫回应说，她的艺名是她在“酗酒的青少年”时编造的。</p><p>当另一位粉丝问她应该“把名字改成什么”时，这位说唱歌手回答说：“只要删除整个帐户并重新考虑一切，永远不会太晚。”</p><p> Doja Cat 最近宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-announces-first-ever-arena-tour-with-support-from-ice-spice-and-doechii-buy-tickets-3460103">她即将举行的 24 场北美“Scarlet”巡演</a>，这是她首次以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doechii">Doechii</a>为伴奏的舞台巡演。该活动将于 10 月 31 日在旧金山大通中心 (Chase Center) 开幕，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fdoja-cat-tickets%2Fartist%2F2062205" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-unveils-her-next-single-attention-in-creepy-video-teaser-3456527">这位歌手发行了新歌《Attention》</a> ，这是她即将发行的专辑中的主打单曲， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-returns-with-new-song-and-video-paint-the-town-red-3478155">本月又发行了《Paint The Town Red》</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-says-she-feels-free-after-losing-social-media-followers-3484293">Doja Cat 表示失去社交媒体粉丝后她感到“自由”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
